data.description: This hidden gem is tucked amidst the trees on a private 0.8-acre lot in the established Cambridge neighborhood of Bremen. Remodeled  in 2020, the interior includes 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a separate home office on the main level. The Kitchen was completely  redesigned in 2020 and features a custom hood range, display cabinets, and a walk-in pantry. The home sits on an unfinished basement with  loads of storage space and potential. The exterior is complete with a fenced-in back yard, covered deck, private patio, and a second  paved driveway leading to the back of the house. The Covered Deck was upgraded in 2022 with high ceilings, covered beams, and a  brand new staircase that overlooks scenic wooded surroundings.
